      <div class=3D"product__header">
        <h1>Campfire <span class=3D"version"><a href=3D"https://once.com/ca=
mpfire/changelog">1.1.2</a></span></h1>
        <h2>Super simple group chat, without a subscription. And you get th=
e code, too.</h2>
        <p>If you=E2=80=99ve used Slack or Teams, you already know how to c=
hat with Campfire. Pay once, download, run one command, and host your whole=
 company on your own server. It=E2=80=99s yours.</p>
      </div>

